data.description: Furnishings for sale as well.  Spectacular 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath in Griffin Park. This home has an attractive open floor plan with a two story living area, gas fireplace and lots of natural lighting. Main floor master with en-suite and a walk in closet. Kitchen has upgraded cabinets, subway tile, wood flooring and ss appliances. Second floor has a bonus loft, two bedrooms, full bath and laundry room. Attached two car garage and plenty of storage.  Community has a nice pool with fireplace and wooded walking trails. A must see!!!
